{"tid":1073900,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【薩莉亞】沙律現曱甴死屍　事主：「最慘係食到最後先見到」","createTime":"2019-03-23T04:22:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-23T10:13:19.000Z","uid":22675,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"64f0550164171fcbb2828b606fd5e480e6e2050f","tid":1073900,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T04:22:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2578370/org/c8bd3246174119c6e5cf84988c7d38e1.jpg/7CfXGkfIr_mxgBdNEEA47coeaur4enRZkYAnsZGAJ7E?v=w800r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2578370%2Forg%2Fc8bd3246174119c6e5cf84988c7d38e1.jpg%2F7CfXGkfIr_mxgBdNEEA47coeaur4enRZkYAnsZGAJ7E%3Fv%3Dw800r16_9&h=df6f8397&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n稱得上是平民意大利菜的薩莉亞意式餐廳是不少人的心水抵食之選，3月19日有網民在討論區開post「薩莉亞隨沙津（律）送小強」，事主稱「最慘係食到最後先見到」。<br />\n從事主照片中可清晰見到一隻「小強」觸肢健全在沙律菜上已經反肚，狀甚嘔心令人錯愕。據留言指涉事餐廳為慈雲山分店，事主稱「叫店長出黎（嚟）解釋，連影都冇隻，個經理理都冇理過我，坐咗係（喺）度半個鐘等個店長，啲staff淨係識講幫我退錢，其實唔係錢嘅問題啊！係食物質素嘅問題啊！」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2576793/org/a31bf15aae32af19a4e7e2f02bb48515.JPG/X43sYJOMdnntxXNxj2y-mHhIwKb0KzqqFRZsAhUWbAI?v=w480\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2576793%2Forg%2Fa31bf15aae32af19a4e7e2f02bb48515.JPG%2FX43sYJOMdnntxXNxj2y-mHhIwKb0KzqqFRZsAhUWbAI%3Fv%3Dw480&h=e0db446e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n記者致電慈雲山薩莉亞分店查詢事件，諮詢組長陳小姐稱有關衛生或深入問題待總公司回應，舖頭每星期有3次滅蟲，覆蓋堂食區及廚房，由滅蟲公司負責。當天事主發現沙津有曱甴，店舖有職員即時處理及安排退款，而事主即場回覆OK。<br />\n<br />\n【食物安全】油甘魚藏多條40cm紅綫蟲！誤食可致胃痛腹瀉（慎入）<br />\n爭鮮三文魚壽司疑現幼蟲　事主稱涉事店覆：下次換過盒<br />\n【食物安全】美婦吃生蠔身體潰爛21天終不治　食肉菌入侵4大渠道<br />\n餐廳衛生蟲害問題一向備受關注，一些走大眾化路線，以實惠價錢作招徠，食客便能享日本、意大利菜質素的食物，但連鎖食肆接二連三出現蟲害，繼早前西環「爭鮮」三文魚壽司被發現有蟲，今次有網民投訴薩莉亞沙律有蟑螂，引起網民熱議。類似事態反映餐廳食品的衛生及食物安全問題惹公眾關注，同時讓人思考餐飲業界的衛生監管措施是否足夠，能否減少漏網之魚保障食用安全。"},{"pid":"b3507202e42000984aa74bfebaeff3cb625102f5","tid":1073900,"uid":55597,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T04:50:55.000Z","msg":"發現 windows 中左毒，事主：「最慘係藍畫先知」"},{"pid":"53fe018601f2b95587d90a56c3a070e29a7974b0","tid":1073900,"uid":42188,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T04:52:24.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">1分錢，1分貨</span></span>"},{"pid":"bb325329124e6a3e101578a38f7e4418627ef289","tid":1073900,"uid":42188,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T04:55:22.000Z","msg":"抵死啦，一邊食野一邊掛住玩手機<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d55c8ef98816b1ac7a9d92c96378cec27e06cb41","tid":1073900,"uid":60594,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T04:56:59.000Z","msg":"最慘你食完見唔到"},{"pid":"0f2153715e94d30f5b89a62f4b71dd09efea27d9","tid":1073900,"uid":137896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T05:07:02.000Z","msg":"連登&gt;公海&gt;連登"},{"pid":"75e80fe4cd8839ba823b27e45d39a8708a746596","tid":1073900,"uid":2054,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T05:08:31.000Z","msg":"免費提供蛋白質<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4af44d7e37702a26a312081178e668776a17203","tid":1073900,"uid":5557,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"bb325329124e6a3e101578a38f7e4418627ef289","tid":1073900,"uid":42188,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T04:55:22.000Z","msg":"抵死啦，一邊食野一邊掛住玩手機<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T05:46:34.000Z","msg":"傻撚左？ 鋪頭衛生有問題唔屌 ，屌個食客。 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0eac8873440b0325c712fb4f72867ea859fa6ac","tid":1073900,"uid":222791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"repl